{"tid":1185131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利迷75萬 Vs 鏝迷10萬　利迷：大細球會嘅分別","createTime":"2019-06-04T05:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T05:36:45.000Z","uid":4661,"like":108,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"105add9f03ba059da0f59014a3e9e070e3502c3f","tid":1185131,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190604/photo/bkn-20190604051500640-0604_00882_001_01p.jpg?20190604054020\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190604%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190604051500640-0604_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20190604054020&h=606bb55c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利物浦剛於歐洲登頂，於歐聯決賽以2:0擊敗熱刺奪標，利物浦球迷開心到癲，將決賽舉行之地馬德里變為利市一樣。一班奪標英雄將大耳朵盃帶返英國，周日舉行勝利大巡遊，總共有75萬人上街大事慶祝，到處人山人海，場面墟冚到爆。 <br />\n<br />\n有利迷之後於網上出Post，將紅軍勝利巡遊盛況，同曼城奪得英超之後嘅巡遊作比較，因為當日藍月亮巡遊，只得10萬人慶祝，同紅軍人數相比差一大截，即時變得好似小貓3、4隻一樣。呢位利迷表示，呢個就係大球會同細球會嘅分別，仲話紅軍對利迷嚟講係一種宗教，曼城對球迷嚟講只係嗜好，當中有天淵之別咁話。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190604/photo/bkn-20190604051500640-0604_00882_001_02p.jpg?20190604054020\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190604%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190604051500640-0604_00882_001_02p.jpg%3F20190604054020&h=38751c74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5df9f1f9708a21651f6f9cb080aedba00f1d1b1b","tid":1185131,"uid":7715,"like":135,"dislike":1,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"3年後仲係度先講野"},{"pid":"a5adf1bc12ec2e3e92004d31a152ab754dd941b2","tid":1185131,"uid":86246,"like":48,"dislike":6,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:47:07.000Z","msg":"因為比曼聯分薄左"},{"pid":"719134b9d2b0cf459374ca94afa7678fb0bdcc90","tid":1185131,"uid":196924,"like":304,"dislike"